title: Reimbursement for Setup Costs
body:
Should each of the vroomDAO other seven members reimburse trunzo.eth for start up costs regarding vroomDAO?

Start up costs: 0.208639212 ETH (0.0260799 ETH per member).

The following link is a full accounting: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1qlo3mcuDcVJQbgBnnTwckyIg4DOw33thPImIz9OoW70/edit?usp=sharing

If anyone needs screenshot receipts from Metamask before voting, please DM trunzo.eth on Discord.
